hello I'm sashikant A Cloud support
engineer here at the AWS office in
Sydney today I'll show you what to do if
you didn't receive a call from AWS to
verify your new account or the pin that
you have entered doesn't work let's get
started first let's verify the following
you entered your telephone number and
selected your country code correctly
during the sign up process
if you are using a mobile phone you are
sure that you have a cellular signal to
receive SMS messages or calls the
information that you have entered for
your payment method is correct a valid
payment method is required to complete
the account activation you have made
sure that the pin that you have entered
is correct if you entered the number
into your phone's keypad and that didn't
work you tried speaking the numbers
instead now I will show you how to retry
the phone verification open the aw supp
console and then choose create case
choose account and billing support for
service select account
activation for category select phone
verification for CT select general
question then click
next in subject use account
activation in the description section
write need assistance with new account
activation share your preferred call
back numbers and time in the the
recommended
sections choose next Sol now or contact
us choose contact us select your
preferred option to contact choose
submit a support case will be created
and you will receive a call back on the
number provided by an aw support
representative note if you still can't
complete the verification process then
AWS support can help you to activate
your account manually be sure that you
can be reached on the telephone number
that you have provided for your AWS
account also you can create a case with
AWS support even if your account isn't
activated yet and now you know what to
do if you didn't receive a call from AWS
to verify your new account or the pin
that you have entered doesn't
work thanks for watching and happy cloud
computing from all of us here at AWS
